It will be assumed by our technology and connected to merchants. SGPay needs to build on the Ethereum blockchain thus it brings benefits such as decentralization, security, clarity and gives you lower prices for the transaction.   Many companies select the blockchain networks such as Microsoft and UBS those who are part of Enterprise Ethereum Alliance. SGPay is the 3rd generation uses e-wallet and e-payment mobile application so that users can buy and sell cryptocurrencies, or if you want to purchase can use both cryptocurrencies and fiat currencies. Main aim is to make the SGPay rules both e-wallet and e-payments those who are staying in Singapore. By using SGPay customers can pay their groceries, can buy tickets, book flight tickets. SGRewards will bond with SGPay platform will help you in giving reward points SGFund that will help to expand small and medium enterprises.

Author: wiserico
Title: ⚡ [ANN] ⚡ SGPAY ⚡ 🚀 BANKING ON A COLLABORATIVE FUTURE PAYMENTS PLATFORM🚀
Body: SGPay has been added to WISERICO tracker    Vote for the SGPay on WISERICO and follow SGPay on the  media platforms:  Telegram Twitter Facebook Medium   Singapore has been a hotbed of blockchain projects in the past year, resulting in successful Singapore-born cryptocurrencies such as DigixDao and Kyber Network. A call has been made by the Singapore Prime Minister Lee Hsien Loong to “simplify and integrate” e-payment services. SGPay is one such project borne from the ideas of innovation and integration. It aims to integrate numerous services into one platform, a digital wallet service for both cryptocurrencies and fiat currencies. Our SGPay Token is built on the Ethereum blockchain in accordance with the ERC-20 standard. The SGPay Token (or SGP in short) is built as a utility token to be used on our primary platform SGPay. It will be adopted by our technology partners and affiliated merchants. We chose to build SGP on the Ethereum blockchain because it brings advantages such as decentralization, security, transparency and lower transaction costs. It is also the preferred blockchain network of many large corporations such as Microsoft and UBS who are part of the Enterprise Ethereum Alliance.  WISERICO on BITCOINTALK

Title: ⚡ [ANN] ⚡ SGPAY ⚡ 🚀 BANKING ON A COLLABORATIVE FUTURE PAYMENTS PLATFORM🚀
Body: Be rewarded for holding our tokens with lower transactional fees for buying and selling cryptocurrencies on our wallet.  Use SGPay Tokens alongside other major cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin for payments or transfers.  Our tokens are classified as utility tokens as they do not provide rights, dividends or liabilities typically associated with shareholders. This provides legal protection for token holders.  The company stakeholders are largely compensated in terms of tokens. Therefore, there is great incentive to increase the underlying token asset value.
